I guess there is a relation in that one creates the jack and the other will disable it when needed.Â  Might need to have a respective enable API, because I believe there are some situations during PM suspend where a jack may want to be disabled and re-enabled on PM resume.
>> +
>> +Returns 0 on success, negative otherwise.
